            "description": "<div id=\"newsBody\">\n<span class=\"newsDetail\" style=\"font-size: 13px; font-family:MingLiu;Arial;\">&lt;汇港通讯&gt;      欧洲股市早段个别发展。英国富时100指数报9,209.65点，跌7.17点(0.08%)；德国DAX指数报24,045.30点，升5.38点(0.02%)；法国CAC 40指数报7,763.90点，升1.30点(0.02%)。 (WL)</span>\n</div>",
