            "title": "深证创指全日收报2890.13点升2.23%",
            "description": "<div id=\"newsBody\">\n<span class=\"newsDetail\" style=\"font-size: 13px; font-family:MingLiu;Arial;\">&lt;汇港通讯&gt;    深证创业板指数全日收报2890.13点，升2.23%。</span>\n</div>",
            "pub_date": "2025-08-29 15:15:33",
